<plot>The film is the story of a theatre actor (Paolo) and the problems he encounters when his girlfriend (Celine) dreams became part of his reality. Her dreams are lived by him in such force that he can no longer distinguish them from his everyday reality. He becomes the victim of her dreams and the help that is offered by his lover - psychiatrist (Deborah) is useless.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?159611</url></doc>
